## Roadmap

### Short-term

* Per-user memory commands — `/memorylist <user>`, `/memoryclear <user>`
* Persona gallery in the wiki

### Medium-term

* Multi-model support — swap providers via env variable
* Conversation channel mention/reply filtering
* Message claiming system for multi-instance deployments

### Long-term

* Knowledge base — `/kbadd`, `/kblist`, `/kbdelete`
* Web dashboard via FastAPI — `fastapi_server.py` is already in the repo
